OL,5, Actress Rose Ayling-Ellis is calling   
OL,6, for sign language lessons to be made   
OL,7, freely available to those who need them
OL,8, - such as the parents and guardians of 
OL,9, deaf children. The current funding for 
OL,10, sign language tuition has been         
OL,11, described as inconsistent and          
OL,12, insufficient.                          
OL,14,F"Being deaf is not something that you  
OL,15,Fovercome, it's something that you      
OL,16,Fembrace," says Rose Ayling-Ellis.      
